licensemanager_grants.name:
(Required) Name of the field to filter by, as defined by
  [the underlying AWS API](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/license-manager/latest/APIReference/API_ListReceivedGrants.html#API_ListReceivedGrants_RequestSyntax).
  For example, if filtering using `ProductSKU`, use:

```terraform
data "aws_licensemanager_grants" "selected" {
  filter {
    name   = "ProductSKU"
    values = [""] # insert values here
  }
}
```

ebs_volumes.name:
(Required) Name of the field to filter by, as defined by
  [the underlying AWS API](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/APIReference/API_DescribeVolumes.html).
  For example, if matching against the `size` filter, use:

```terraform
data "aws_ebs_volumes" "ten_or_twenty_gb_volumes" {
  filter {
    name   = "size"
    values = ["10", "20"]
  }
}
```

